ISLAMABAD, Sep 29 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Tuesday appointed Maulana Tahir Mehmood Ashrafi as Special Representative of the Prime Minister on Religious Harmony with immediate effect.
According to a press release of Prime Minister Office Media Wing, the appointment of Maulana Ashrafi would be in honourary capacity.
